{"tid":315405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶鬧交飛武士刀落街無辜女途人被劈頭","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T08:07:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9375a753538ab129394141f84316f65e15174f3","tid":315405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:58:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084867&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084867%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&d=f%2BQVzLxqOPmwvy0z%2BjW7LsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=d015c8fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084867%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&h=72d9d2ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084867&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710</a><br />\n<br />\n情侶鬧交飛武士刀落街<br />\n無辜女途人被劈頭<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n實在很恐怖！浙江寧波一名女子，日前在當地一個屋苑行走時，突然被一件從天而降的物體擊中，當場暈倒，途人見狀將她送院，而將她擊暈的，竟是一把長90厘米的武士刀。當局稱幸武士刀從天而降時，撞到牆壁改變方向，刀鋒未有碰到女子，所以她能保一命。<br />\n<br />\n這名女子姓韓，她說本月1日晚她在一個屋苑行走時，「突然間就暈過去了，後來模模糊糊有點意識，我就摸了一下自己的頭，發現有一個口子裂開來了」，途人發現她暈倒後馬上召喚救護車，將她送院，她的頭部傷，要縫8針。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方接報後場調查，發現將韓女擊暈的，竟是一把長90厘米的武士刀，警員於是上樓逐家逐戶搜查，在一個11樓的單位發現一個刀鞘，與武士刀匹配，於是將刀主拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被補的是一名姓陸，來自貴州、現年20歲的女子，她與男友今年初搬到這單位，當日下午她與男友因瑣事吵架，約7時許男友拿下武士刀，想拿刀嚇一下女友，讓她停止發脾氣，陸女於是出手搶刀，混亂期間武士刀便飛出窗外，擊中在樓下走過的韓女。<br />\n<br />\n警方以「危險行為危害公共安全罪」將陸女刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n《寧波晚報》"},{"pid":"603d8609db4a1a034a9574c05b1b9fa0d4abe869","tid":315405,"uid":12190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"屌 好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259d7389d35fc6e3e24935fc67ecaee776ee0388","tid":315405,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"諗起索隆"},{"pid":"f3dd9c92267db450a725bb2dd2477a26c0d5f17c","tid":315405,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"條仔做pt 武士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fddcfef49d5d471e82b3ee4877cd26c96f0cf8","tid":315405,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae93b8e4b38153e7cee15ac99bd826013068736","tid":315405,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"最後武士"},{"pid":"387a720f11c271e1c4b3d5277f0ecc75d5461590","tid":315405,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起索隆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6418ff3295e7fcabe024c28ea6bfe5882f31bc9","tid":315405,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條仔做pt 武士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i3pdk0a9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi3pdk0a9&h=5c030880&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c93b61336a5e9bc1f72bbd105a938367df408a5c","tid":315405,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"黑武士"}]}